-- FR-9 example community runs (verifiable via the SearchPage 'Verify' button).
--
-- Derived from the owner's annotated traverse_api_input scenarios. Generated by
-- running buildSimInputs -> Driver -> summarizeEngine over the committed real
-- fixtures (src/simulation/__fixtures__/real/) and emitting submit_run(...) for
-- each full clear. Idempotent: submit_run upserts on
-- (quest_id, servant_collection_nos, np_levels) and only overwrites on a lower
-- total_np_cost, so re-applying is safe.
--
-- Excluded: the kazuradrop "statistical clear" scenario (373/426/421/426,
-- q94095710) aborts at the wave-1 end-turn — the engine's Kukulkan (373) NP
-- under-kills the 181,138-HP 金剛巨人像 (~71k dealt), short of the annotation's
-- expected easy clear (missing class advantage / anti-Earth SE / S1 optional
-- buff). Re-add once Kukulkan's matchup is modeled.

